Package com.putable.siteriter.example

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExampleConnection
    A sample concrete class extending AbstractConnection, which see for an overview of its purpose.
    ExampleConnectionFactory
    This implementation of a ConnectionFactory builds ExampleConnection's and passes them the SDLParser reference the factory got when it was built.
    ExampleSDLParserImpl
    A totally-non-spec-correct stub SDLParser implementation, so that the ExampleServer can have something to use.
    ExampleServer
    An example web server based on the com.putable.siteriter.server classes, available as a example, model, and starting point for modification by UNM CS351 S'10 students to build their own server code.
